            <h1>19/10/2022</h1>
            <p>The Department of Information Science at Stellenbosch University will host the 51st Annual Conference of the Southern African Computer Lecturers’ Association (SACLA 2022) on 21 and 22 July 2022 in Cape Town, South Africa. The conference, which is planned to be an in-person event, provides a forum for the discussion of original research and practical experiences in teaching and learning of Information Systems, Computer Science, Information Technology and related disciplines, as well as the use of software tools in support of education more broadly. The conference programme will include research paper sessions, plenary keynote addresses, panels and workshops.</p>
